=3D"wixui-rich-text__text"><p class=3D"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span =
class=3D"wixui-rich-text__text">In crochet patterns, brackets [ ] indicate =
that a group of stitches should be repeated a certain number of times. For =
example, "[sc5, 2sc] 4 times" means you should single crochet5 consecutivel=
y, then complete 2 single crochets in the same place, and repeat that seque=
nce 4 times.&nbsp;Brackets help simplify longer sets of instructions by kee=
